entries.femaleVariant: Sorry, wrong room.
Oh, sorry. Wrong room.
About that... Once you made the backup, can you tweak it to remove... undesirable traits?
I know you don't often agree to use the Relic, but... well, you don't usually make an engram of a living person, either.
'Cause Lizzy... ever since her conversion, she... she hasn't been herself.
But... how significant would these edits be?
Significant. Sometimes... Sometimes I don't even recognize her. Other times...
'Ey! What the hell are you doing here?!
Eh, never mind. Let's have a drink. To our partnership.
Champagne? Nice surprise.
Very wrong. Get lost, before I call security.
Snoopin' on you, Liam.
Lizzy sent me.
Argh, fucking hell... No privacy.
Get the hell out. Or I'm gonna call security.
Isn't it obvious, Liam? Listenin' in on you two.
entries.maleVariant: Oh, isn't it obvious, Liam? Listenin' in on you two.

entries.femaleVariant: Security! Intruder! Over here!
Lizzy. Y'know, your output.
The one you wanna put on a shard... without her knowledge.
Oh, so that's how you make problems disappear, huh? Throw money at 'em... And poof – they're gone.
entries.maleVariant: Oh, so that's how you make your problems disappear, huh? Throw money at 'em... And poof – they're gone.

entries.femaleVariant: No way.
You ordered champagne?
Uh... you ordered champagne?
Yes. And we'd like to enjoy it in peace.
OK. Eddies, please.
Sure, send me cred. Better be a lot.
Sure, sure. I get it! Transferring now.
Uh, consider it a token of my gratitude.
Aw, come on... Arasaka's taken a keen interest in Lizzy's career.
Oh, OK. Sorry, system said the order was still open...
I couldn't give two fucks about your system. Get out.
Huh? Who sent you? Tell me – now!
Not here to talk to you.
Wouldn't you like to know? Well, chill. All in good time.
I'll tell whoever needs told about you two lovebirds... Expect things to heat up.
She'll be interested to hear about this chat of yours. Very interested.
Hey, hey! Wait! Wait one fucking second!
Listen, I'll... I'll pay you, OK? Whatever you want. Just... forget everything you heard, all right?
Oh, fuck... You heard what I just heard, right?
Uh-huh. Guy's cheatin'. Bet my life.
entries.maleVariant: Huh. Guy's cheatin'. Bet my life.

entries.femaleVariant: Dunno... I mean, he's up to somethin', no doubt... But that back there? That was about somethin' else.
Yeah, minor detes. Either way, she'd better keep away from him.
entries.maleVariant: Minor detes. Either way, she'd better keep away from him.

entries.femaleVariant: Relic... They wanna do her like they did me...
I'm afraid that's impossible. Engrams saved in the Secure Your Soul program cannot be edited.
Tell me why you're doing this.
Sure, maybe I'll say yes. But first, wanna hear your why.
Liam, no. Arasaka was very clear--
Fuck Arasaka.
I'm afraid for her. Lizzy... she wanted to go full conversion, right? Change her whole body to chrome. She did it... but something went wrong.
At first, it was just little memory problems, concentration, but now... She's changed.
We all change, Liam. All the time. Usually for the worse.
You don't get it. When I talk to her, I'm scared. There's something... something in her. Shit, I can't describe it.
It's fine. I'm not the one you owe an explanation.
No, wait, wai--! I'll pay whatever you want, just don't tell anybody. I am begging you.
I'm out. Oh, and drink up. Bubbly's no good warm.
entries.maleVariant: I'm out. And drink up. Bubbly's no good warm.

entries.femaleVariant: 'Fraid it won't work this time.
Be a shame if it ended prematurely. A backup copy seems to be the most sensible solution.
Not exactly. They wiped you. Here, they just wanna make a backup.
A backup! V... we're talkin' about a person, not your vacay snaps. Guy didn't even ask, he's just going behind her back.
He's got no right to do it. Nobody has that right.
She might not take you at your word.
Uh-huh. That's why I gotta klep the security cam footage.
Specially without her knowing. Ah shit... How do I even tell her?
entries.maleVariant: Specially without her knowing. Shit... How do I even tell her?

entries.femaleVariant: Don't have to. Camera in there... Where there's a cam, there's footage.
Look, I don't know who you are, but I can assure you – you'll regret this.
Risk of regret must be why they're payin' me.
